@startuml Reconciliation Pipeline

actor User
participant CLI
participant Parser
participant Normalizer
participant Matcher
participant Classifier
participant Reporter

User -> CLI: run reconcile
CLI -> Parser: load(internal, external)
Parser -> Normalizer: normalize to Canonical Model
Normalizer -> Matcher: execute matching
Matcher -> Classifier: classify unmatched records
Matcher -> Reporter: send matches
Classifier -> Reporter: send exceptions
Reporter -> User: write output files

@enduml
